we have two top line dots now, wd and bor.  why oh why would you replace the higher damage higher level one and keep the lower level lower damage one?  that would be just silly.  look at it as a function of damage over time.  replacing bor instead of wd, our damage would be 387 damage higher per minute.  that adds up over time to be a great deal.<br>
