<br>
i'm alteration spec, another dot of whichever line will be the same mana-wise to me as long as they are the same efficiency.  however i also realize half of us are evoc spec, so they would get a big bonus from any new dot being from the fire line.  it also makes more sense to use the line that will give 50% of us a mana savings, rather than use the line that will give less about 0.01% of us mana savings.<br>
<br>
